Tool Link: https://github.com/wifiphisher/wifiphisher

##Installing WifiPhisher
1. Get the latest release from github repo. Avoid clone, it may be broken
2. Goto directory and run
	sudo python setup.py install
3. You can use tool via 
	wifiphisher


#Installing Additional Scenarios 

Repo: https://github.com/wifiphisher/extra-phishing-pages

1. Move the scenario folder to {wifiphisher_dir}/wifiphisher/data/phishing-pages
2. Run 
	sudo python setup.py install
3. Done !
